        "text": "Deuteronomy 31:10-13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " now took place. The observance was perhaps a new thing to the newly-formed community, and is therefore recorded with so much emphasis. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "They kept the feast seven days",
        "children": []
