        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". By \"according to the manner\" seems to be meant \"according to the regularly established custom\"- one proof out of many that the feast had been constantly observed, though not perhaps with all the proper ceremonies (see the comment on ver. 17). ",
